                            <p>
            Settlements are the process by which your transaction funds are transferred to your linked bank account. Understanding the settlement cycle helps you manage cash flow effectively. </p>
                            <h3>Settlement Cycle</h3>
                            <p>The standard settlement process follows this timeline:</p>  -->
                    <!-- Settlement timeline visual 
